[This is South Korea's 11th FMDV serotype O outbreak in 2010, and the 3rd
on its mainland. For a summary of the 2 previous outbreaks on the mainland
(in CH'UNGCH'ONG-BUKDO or Chungcheongbuk-do and CH'UNGCH'ONG-NAMDO or
Chungcheongnam-do), and a map showing their respective locations, see
<http://www.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=9166>. -
Mod.AS]
